whose contents is extracted.
.ti -\w'\(em'u
\(emunpacking of multi-part uuencoded files, which produce a *.zip archive
whose contents is listed.
.ti -\w'\(em'u
\(emunpacking of multi-part uuencoded files, which produce a *.zip archive
whose contents is extracted.
.ti -\w'\(em'u
\(emunpacking of multi-part uuencoded files, which produce a *.lha archive
